  "title": "HOUSE OFFICER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>Summer View Hotel boasts 86 designer furnished guest rooms. It is ideally located in the heart of Singapore. Transport is facilitated by close proximity of Rochor MRT Station (3-minute walk) and easy availability of public transports (Bus and Taxi) to any part of Singapore.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will assist in fulfilling guest requests and support multiple hotel departments to maintain a clean, safe, and welcoming environment for guests and staff.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Respond promptly to guest requests by delivering room amenities and other services to enhance guest satisfaction</li><li>Collaborate with Housekeeping, Front Office, and Security teams to support daily hotel operations and ensure smooth service delivery</li><li>Maintain the cleanliness, neatness, and safety of the hotel lobby area throughout your shift</li><li>Follow instructions from Supervisors or Managers to complete additional tasks that support hotel operations</li><li>Apply any prior security experience to contribute to the safety and security of hotel premises</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information</strong></p><ul><li>Work schedule: 4 working days per week</li></ul>",
